<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/61406298-lee-bartholomew">Lee Bartholomew</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Apparently Dec 2000 in Cedar Rapids IA at a B&amp;N there. Musta been a christmas present :) Although there is no book 6. This is inspired by the Pendrago<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Apparently Dec 2000 in Cedar Rapids IA at a B&amp;N there. Musta been a christmas present :) Although there is no book 6. This is inspired by the Pendragon cycle supposedly. But The Pendragon Cycle is still a 5 book series. Which ended with Grail. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
